headline: CHIPOTLE ANNOUNCES FREE DOUBLE PROTEIN OFFER ON TUESDAY, JANUARY 13 TO POWER PROTEIN GOALS
summary: Chipotle Mexican Grill (NYSE: CMG) today announced a free double protein offer on bowls, burritos and salads1 on Tuesday, January 13, one of the most popular days to work out.2 With consumers prioritizing active lifestyles in January, Chipotle is curating its menu and offerings to help guests hit their fitness and dietary goals.

thumbnail.caption: Chipotle's Double High Protein Bowl (81g protein, 11g fiber, 760 calories) features double Adobo Chicken, light white rice, black beans, fajita veggies, fresh tomato salsa, Monterey Jack cheese and extra romaine lettuce.
